title: Intel Meteor Lake Ultra 7 155H Hands On, An Edge Over The Rest! MSI Prestige 16 AI Evo
description:
Intel's Meteor Lake is here, and it's promising to revolutionize the way we experience laptops. The Core Ultra 7 155H is the top-of-the-line chip in this new lineup, and it's packed with cutting-edge features that make it perfect for power users and creative professionals. The MSI Prestige 16 AI Evo is a powerhouse laptop that's packed with the latest and greatest technology, including Intel's new Meteor Lake processors. In this hands-on video, we'll take a closer look at the design, performance, and features of this impressive machine with a beautiful 16” 4K HDR OLED Screen. This Video Is sponsored by Micro Center.
